# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺股市入面，當股票跌到一定程度嘅時候，投資者會賣出股票，以阻止損失再大嘅行為。（通常用喺股市討論）
eng:to cut losses (in stock market)
<eg>
yue:呢隻股票跌到仆街，我唯有止蝕。 (ni1 zek3 suk1 gou3 dit1 dou3 paak3 gaai1, ngo5 wai6 jau6 zi3 sik1.)
eng:This stock has plummeted, I have no choice but to cut losses.

yue:止蝕唔係一件容易嘅事，因為人心理上唔想承認自己嘅錯誤。 (zi3 sik1 m4 hai6 jat1 gin3 ngai6 san1 ge3 si4, jan1 wai4 jan4 seon3 ge3 zi6 gaak3.)
eng:Cutting losses isn't an easy thing, because psychologically, people don't want to admit their mistakes.
